A LoRA Model of Elysia from Honkai Impact 3rd.

This LoRA includes Three official costumes.

Recommend 0.85-1 Strength for triggering any official costume.

For changing custom clothes, I suggest 0.7-0.9 Weight

The preview images were generated by the AbyssOrangeMix series Model.

I am using the NAI model [e6e8e1fc] to train. Able to work with all mixed models based on NAI(i.e. AbyssOrangeMix, Anything v3)

Enjoy it!
